TCS Al Fridays Hackathon
Title:
Media Copyright Query Resolution Agent
Problem Statement:
Media companies must navigate complex copyright laws; content creators need quick answers on usage rights.
Data Requirements:
Copyright law texts, media company policies, and licensing agreements.
(Feel free to generate synthetic data as well from the provided access)
Expected Output:
Natural language explanations of copyright rules, usage permissions, and recommended actions.
Be creative to go beyond as you solve the above needs
